  "onboardingWelcomeCopyShort": "Thanks for trying Compartarenta.\n\nThe app is free as long as it isn’t actively used. During this phase, you can configure your expense-sharing plan as precisely as you need. This plan will serve as a proposed agreement to share with one or more people.\n\nOnce your plan is accepted and put into service, the 6‑week free trial begins.",
